{"tid":1253674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察深夜出PO諗住引你班群龍無首既柒頭圍警總","createTime":"2019-06-23T16:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T14:31:50.000Z","uid":88743,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fcb155046eb90169922213a082156587617710a1","tid":1253674,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:46:06.000Z","msg":"就各界關注警察在醫院行使警權，警方現作以下回應：<br />\n<br />\n根據香港法例第232章警隊條例第50條，如警務人員合理地相信有人干犯可被判處監禁的罪行或在訂明的情況下，便可作出拘捕。另外，即使該警務人員沒有為此而發出的手令，亦可行使拘捕的權力。<br />\n<br />\n所有急症室警崗每日均有警員二十四小時當值，負責為急症室醫護人員與警方單位聯絡。如有由醫護人員轉介需注意的個案（例如，懷疑傷勢是在牽涉刑事成分的事件中造成），當值警員會進行初步調查，然後把報告交由相關警方單位跟進。另外，如果駐守急症室的警員在急症室大堂發現有求診者(包括受害人或疑犯)懷有可疑的傷勢，警方亦會主動跟進相關案件。警方亦會在不同的情況下到醫院工作，包括在收到報案後到醫院向報案人或相關人士了解情況、了解受害人或涉案人士的傷勢及安排被捕人士到醫院接受治療等。<br />\n<br />\n警方在醫院調查任何個案或進行任何行動時，並不會阻礙任何人士接受治療，同時絕對尊重病人私隱，以及任何人士應有的其他權利，包括聘請法律代表。<br />\n<br />\n任何人士如對警方有任何指控，歡迎向警方提供具體證據以作跟進。對於一些沒有事實根據的指控，警方表示遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日你地想圍政總 但佢引你地去圍警總<br />\n你地會點揀?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />政總<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />警總"},{"pid":"4d4296c27b2da103994c3707ab4d08f55bb19a0b","tid":1253674,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:51:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c893b871f923fe6e49bef809e22b84b9169d60","tid":1253674,"uid":122988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:54:04.000Z","msg":"沒有事實根據的指控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />砌開生豬肉既人咁講"},{"pid":"322d0813c9e87758ae3053b9203af888a2d6cd7e","tid":1253674,"uid":88743,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://themetapicture.com/media/funny-government-people-protest-police-comic.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthemetapicture.com%2Fmedia%2Ffunny-government-people-protest-police-comic.jpg&h=53abb8be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f28f36f03d1e7b569e59c914c7a997910409cf03","tid":1253674,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:00:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c076f8113116c3a3f72aea9415d4a1c05e2cd481","tid":1253674,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:11:25.000Z","msg":"聽朝我估警察可能會搵條友出黎廢UP引鳩你地圍警總<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13144cb7e5c6955b92332000296723e972e43b7d","tid":1253674,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:12:40.000Z","msg":"政府呢兩日完全龜縮狀態無左影<br />\n唔知政總聽日會唔會又唔開門<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a778f6236dde9d698820a085246b79cb1b39fd","tid":1253674,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:18:33.000Z","msg":"警力無限大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24749bab03f02839d85dda5bc315483d6a687211","tid":1253674,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T03:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37106612e3ebfa8c7fbf328a70bbdbc20c597c79","tid":1253674,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14:31:50.000Z","msg":"成班柒頭"}]}